      • getDiscussionType

        public String getDiscussionType()
        Type of discussion topic: default(blank), side_comment, threaded. threaded indicates that replies are threaded where side_comment indicates that replies in the discussion are flat. See related Canvas Guide https://guides.instructure.com/m/4152/l/60423-how-do-i-create-a-threaded-discussion
